{
  "stem": "15174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then he went to Krakow, which was the larger city nearby, where his-- one of his married sisters, Ida, lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he got a job there as a tailor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So-- so there-- there we were, my mother and I in Germany alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was terrible for my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was terrible for me, because you know, after all these little experiences and this big experience, I was really very scared.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The-- this deportation of Polish Jewish men from Germany had another side effect, because what happened was there was a young guy living in Paris by the name of Grynszpan whose father had also been deported from Germany back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was infuriated by this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he decided that he was going to do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the something that he was going to do was try to assassinate the-- the German ambassador to Paris.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I guess he did attempt it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I believe that he just wounded one of the attaches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Nobody really got hurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But this served as the pretext for Kristallnacht, which occurred a little over a week later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My father was deported on October 28 and Kristallnacht was the night of November 9th-10th.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember Kristallnacht itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I mean, I guess I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I certainly wasn't outside at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I do remember that I couldn't go to school for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then finally, my mother got word that the school was open again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Now, you-- you have to understand that by that time Jewish children could not go to German schools.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They could only go to-- to Jewish schools, so I was going to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The school that I was at was right next to a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
